partnerships-header = Waayilummaawwan
partnerships-header-text = Common Voice akka mudatu gochuuf waan baay'ee barbaachisaa dha! Kophaa keenya hin raawwannu. Nu waliin michuu ta'uu barbaadduu? Osoo isin irraa dhageenyee ni jaallanna.
